longBusinessSummary: Creative Waste Solutions, Inc., through its subsidiaries, provides waste management environmental services to residential, commercial, industrial, and municipal customers in the United States. It offers waste management brokerage services; and operates waste transfer station that accepts various waste. The company is based in Boca Raton, Florida.
